<title>USA: Universal International seeks financing.</title>
<headline>Universal International seeks financing.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-05-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Universal International Inc said Wednesday it was seeking about $12 million in equity financing to complete the purchase about 90 retail locations of Perry Brothers Inc.</p>
<p>The retailer said it hired Price Waterhouse LLP to help raise the financing.</p>
<p>The company said it planned to offer &quot;a significant equity interest in Universal.&quot;</p>
<p>Universal shares closed down 1/16 at 7/8 Thursday.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
